This year's edition of the annual Nairobi Wine Festival was held on Saturday at the Delta Towers along Waiyaki Way in Nairobi. The event saw a host of renowned wine distributors exhibit their products to the hundreds of guests. Among the distributors were Jos Hansen, Leleshwa Wines inspired by Kenya, Belverde Vodka, King Robert Vodka Rum and Gin, MacAndrews scotch whisky, Hennessy and Protos Wines .The white and black-themed event saw guests turn up in large numbers, as they showcased trendy outfits while enjoying the classy wine-sampling fiesta.